Tongues
Discworld ritual help
Tongues

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Tongues - Grants the priest the gift of speaking in tongues.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
When this miscellaneous ritual is performed, its priest is granted
the gift of tongues, the ability to speak in and understand a
multitude of foreign languages.  The duration of the blessing will
depend on your skill in performing miscellaneous rituals.
.EP
